<subSubSection pageId="4" pageNumber="503" type="discussion">
<paragraph blockId="4.[151,1437,618,1653]" pageId="4" pageNumber="503">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[199,317,1518,1544]" pageId="4" pageNumber="503">Remarks:</emphasis>
The larva of this species was described from 
<collectingCountry box="[838,933,1518,1544]" name="Vietnam" pageId="4" pageNumber="503">Vietnam</collectingCountry>
by Braasch &amp; Soldán (1979). Subsequently, 
<bibRefCitation author="Nguyen, V. V. &amp; Bae, Y. J." box="[151,408,1554,1581]" pageId="4" pageNumber="503" pagination="19 - 28" refId="ref10891" refString="Nguyen, V. V. &amp; Bae, Y. J. (2004) Larvae of the heptageniid mayfly genus Epeorus (Ephemeroptera: Heptageniidae) from Vietnam. Journal of Asia-Pacific Entomology, 7, 19 - 28. https: // doi. org / 10.1016 / S 1226 - 8615 (08) 60197 - 1" type="journal article" year="2004">Nguyen &amp; Bae (2004)</bibRefCitation>
redescribed the larva of 
<taxonomicName authorityName="Braasch &amp; Soldan" authorityYear="1979" box="[696,842,1554,1580]" class="Insecta" family="Heptageniidae" genus="Epeorus" kingdom="Animalia" order="Ephemeroptera" pageId="4" pageNumber="503" phylum="Arthropoda" rank="species" species="bifurcatus">
<emphasis box="[696,842,1554,1580]" italics="true" pageId="4" pageNumber="503">E. bifurcatus</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
based also on specimens from 
<collectingCountry box="[1204,1303,1554,1580]" name="Vietnam" pageId="4" pageNumber="503">Vietnam</collectingCountry>
. 
<bibRefCitation author="Braasch, D. &amp; Boonsoong, B." pageId="4" pageNumber="503" pagination="1 - 26" refId="ref10160" refString="Braasch, D. &amp; Boonsoong, B. (2010) A contribution to the Heptageniidae (Insecta, Ephemeroptera) of Thailand and Malaysia. Zootaxa, 2610, 1 - 26. https: // doi. org / 10.11646 / zootaxa. 2610.1.1" type="journal article" year="2010">Braasch &amp; Boonsoong (2010)</bibRefCitation>
reported this species from 
<collectingCountry box="[660,763,1590,1616]" name="Thailand" pageId="4" pageNumber="503">Thailand</collectingCountry>
; we provide a supplementary larval description based on our material, which represents the first record of the species for 
<collectingCountry box="[824,885,1626,1652]" name="India" pageId="4" pageNumber="503">India</collectingCountry>
.
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
